          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The thermal-neutron fission were obtained by",
                "irradiation of U235 in the thermal column of the Los",
                "Alamos Water Boiler reactor and the resonance",
                "fissions by irradiation of U235 wrapped in 0.0l7 inch",
                "of cadmium metal and located near the central ball of",
                "the reactor. Four observations were made at thermal",
                "fission and two each of resonance fission."
              ]
            }
          ],
